@grunch ,

added a simple function to have last trade index  of a user triggerable from a client.

We will use a new Action called `LastTradeIndex`, clients can request it and they receive the user last trade index stored in `user` table of mostro database, the format is:
```Json
{
  "restore": {
    "version": 1,
    "action": "last-trade-index",
    "trade_index": 42,
    "payload": null
  }
}
```

